{"tid":1201260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵終於出聲喇","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T03:46:19.000Z","uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73261a49cdab0b96980f72b4216bbd3840be4a8e","tid":1201260,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"美國紐約曼哈頓一架直升機降落摩天大樓頂部時墜毀，機師死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期一下午2時左右，直升機墜毀令大樓頂層發生火警，但很快被撲滅。部份工人從大樓撤離，無人受傷。聯邦航空管理局表示，出事時直升機上只有機師一人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紐約州長葛謨說，事件一度引起時報廣場附近民眾恐慌，並聯想起911事件。美國總統特朗普在白宮形容，事故是一場悲劇。"},{"pid":"06dc3ec5e5e86cac1dd7faa33548f0b6ab17757a","tid":1201260,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"216d22d68a6138db770b14fb1071f2cf329b92b1","tid":1201260,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed4b8e1fd2ec9eb34ec6aea778c9ef728e8809cc","tid":1201260,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db682790d3cf899bcd9016cc322d6854c1e527d","tid":1201260,"uid":22628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"今次主題曲 黑色洋紫荊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1201192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1201192</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}